                <head>No. 590<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On August 11, the United States and Japan signed at Tokyo a Civil Air Transport
                    Agreement with an Exchange of Notes relating to provisional application. For
                    text, see 4 <gloss target="#t_UST1">UST</gloss> (pt. 2) 1948.</p>
                <p>Documents on the negotiation of this agreement are principally in file 611.9494
                    for 1952.</p>
            </div>
